OL,3,CResidents in dispute over pothole
OL,4,Crepairs in Scottish Borders
OL,6,FA neighbourhood has been trying to
OL,7,Ffind out who is responsible for
OL,8,Fpothole repairs on their road.
OL,10,FBill and Alison have lived in their
OL,11,Fhome in Burnfoot for 29 years and it
OL,12,Fwas only after receiving a letter from
OL,13,FScottish Borders Housing Association
OL,14,Fin February this year were they told
OL,15,Fthey were responsible for repairing
OL,16,Fthe road alongside other homeowners in
OL,17,Fthe street.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/5
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
