OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,359,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F358A1773846665
OL,3,CResidents in dispute over pothole
OL,4,Crepairs in Scottish Borders
OL,6,FBill Little said: "Being an owner of
OL,7,Fthe property doesn't make me a
OL,8,Fresponsible for a roadway that's
OL,9,Foutside my boundaries. Scottish
OL,10,FBorders Housing Association (SBHA) say
OL,11,Fthey're bringing in surveyors which
OL,12,Fmeans you're talking hundreds of
OL,13,Fthousands of pounds.
OL,15,F"This is not going to be #1,000, to be
OL,16,Fsplit between 6 or 7 residents, that I
OL,17,Fwouldn't have a problem with."
OL,19,FScottish Borders Housing Association
OL,20,Ftook over Scottish Borders Council
OL,21,Fsocial housing in 2003.
OL,26,@nD@SOUwD@AOUyD@^O]
