PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F358A1773846665
OL,3,CResidents in dispute over pothole
OL,4,Crepairs in Scottish Borders
OL,6,FMcLagan Drive in Burnfoot issue up of
OL,7,Fa mix of private homes and social-
OL,8,Frented homes which are managed by SBHA.
OL,10,FSBHA said: "SBHA is assessing the
OL,11,Fcondition of the access road and
OL,12,Fhardstanding area at the garages to
OL,13,Fthe rear of McLagan Drive and Burnfoot
OL,14,FRoad.
OL,16,F"Through a review of Title Deeds, this
OL,17,Fhas been determined as a shared
OL,18,Fmaintenance area involving several
OL,19,Fproperty owners, and increased use
OL,20,Fover time has contributed to its
OL,21,Fdeterioration.
OL,26,@rD@LOU
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/5
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,359,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F358A1773846665
OL,3,CResidents in dispute over pothole
OL,4,Crepairs in Scottish Borders
OL,6,F"We have written to owners to confirm
OL,7,Ftheir shared responsibility for
OL,8,Frepairs, and we are in the process of
OL,9,Fmaking arrangements to meet to discuss
OL,10,Foptions and agree a way forward."
OL,12,FAlison Little said before this
OL,13,Ftransfer the road was maintained by
OL,14,FScottish Borders Council.
OL,16,FShe said: "We've never had any
OL,17,Fcorrespondence whatsoever over all the
OL,18,Fyears to say that the road that we all
OL,19,Fuse is our responsibility. So we
OL,20,Fexpect somebody else to be footing the
OL,21,Fbill, not the owners."
OL,26,@rD@aO]xD@KOU}D@VO]
